Package ru.introguzzle.parsers.common.cache

Class CacheService

java.lang.Object
ru.introguzzle.parsers.common.cache.CacheService
All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable, Executor, ExecutorService, ScheduledExecutorService, CacheSupplier
public final class CacheService extends Object implements ScheduledExecutorService, CacheSupplier
Service class responsible for creating and managing Cache instances. Ensures that all caches of this library share a single ScheduledExecutorService for periodic tasks, such as cache invalidation, to optimize resource usage and maintain consistency.
